{"tid":663152,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"一齊貼直出相","createTime":"2018-05-13T05:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-18T16:52:20.000Z","uid":389,"like":8,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"afb5ac19a0a63aa50dfce669568d448c24c316cb","tid":663152,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T05:12:05.000Z","msg":"見大家成日話人咪精重，決定開返個清泉Post<br />\n唔比落味精純直出<br />\n<br />\n規則：<br />\n1.器材不限<br />\n2.唔可以用電腦或手機後製或加Filter<br />\n3.如果用影相App出前置既Filter,請附上原本既相或講明用咩App咩效果<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/130931_c6f6ff986e60c00d2dba1a5a525c7d75.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F130931_c6f6ff986e60c00d2dba1a5a525c7d75.png&h=e96ba67b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（菲林，Kodak Portra160)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/130931_5c0a520869f8bba9b7820907c114d920.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F130931_5c0a520869f8bba9b7820907c114d920.png&h=1aec5ea3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(電話，iPhone7)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/130932_5c0a520869f8bba9b7820907c114d920.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F130932_5c0a520869f8bba9b7820907c114d920.png&h=f9a5e901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(電話，iPhone7)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/130933_0c9dddd5daaaf521241dddf38ad4f36f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F130933_0c9dddd5daaaf521241dddf38ad4f36f.png&h=d91a67ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(電話，iPhone7)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/13/130933_a11cda42c13c7081dfaefc59cd2f5246.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F13%2F130933_a11cda42c